---

<aside class="lg:col-span-4">
  <div class="bg-[#f6f4e6] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 sticky top-24">
    <h3 class="font-headline text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#2e0007] font-bold mb-6">Buscar Biblioteca</h3>
    <div class="relative mb-8 md:mb-10">
      <input
        class="w-full bg-white border-none rounded-lg py-3 px-4 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#2e0007] text-sm font-body"
        placeholder="Titulo, autor o palabra clave..."
        type="text"
      />
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute right-3 top-3 text-[#897172]">search</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-label text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#564243] mb-4">
          Guia de Envio
        </h4>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-[#564243] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Interesado en publicar con DETRA-UNT? Revisa nuestros criterios de revision por pares y estandares de formato.
        </p>
        <a class="text-xs font-bold text-[#2e0007] underline underline-offset-4" href="#">
          Leer Guias
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pt-6 md:pt-8 border-t border-[#dcc0c1]/30">
        <h4 class="font-label text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#564243] mb-4">
          Boletin
        </h4>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-[#564243] mb-4">
          Recibe los ultimos resumenes de investigacion en tu correo mensualmente.
        </p>
        <input
          class="w-full bg-[#e5e3d5] border-none rounded py-2 px-3 text-sm mb-2"
          placeholder="correo-academico@edu.com"
          type="email"
        />
        <button class="w-full bg-[#2e0007] text-white text-xs font-label py-2 rounded">
          Suscribirse
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>
